rooms.name: The Eldorian Foothills
rooms.description: The hills roll softly and the view is breathtaking.  Small woodland creatures scurry about and you feel at peace in this serene nature.  Open fields can be seen in the distance and a the Great Northern Road passes near here.  Looks like a good spot for a nap.

Looks like a good spot for a nap.  The balck woods trail lay to the north and west.

Open fields can be seen in the distance and the Great Northern Road passes near here.  The hills drop away to the north.  You could climb into the treetops from here if you were daring enough.
